ces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n渣ga</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 儲下氣遲d再挑戰</blockquote><br />\n無謂浪費人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爛片當笑片睇係另類享受</blockquote><br />\n抖M<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家睇搞笑番好多都笑唔出，反而爛片笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1cd7cfdddadcb9d54b23d70439977bf893455d","tid":275693,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>作畫聖劍使神啲 但劇情就魔法戰爭勝一籌</blockquote><br />\n聖劍使當笑片睇應該小勝魔法戰爭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nyes 頭兩集睇到笑到頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n然後無再追<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c65f963d1cffada6695d00cc8bef3c4b09f2b08","tid":275693,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:55:55.000Z","msg":"神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2179b6b65f7e63e5303c28f9061de751f557add","tid":275693,"uid":21000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T10:59:01.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實細佬之前有開過post話想做點評 有巴打叫我睇下神作魔法戰爭先 就小試下牛刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實呢套唔難捱 聖劍使難捱啲 睇完真係會覺得智商小左 但笑片黎講係幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223618972963ca4605ab2a3a9b9a6d6047424f78","tid":275693,"uid":69741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T11:02:49.000Z","msg":"但係我果陣睇維基, 小說好似之後果D卷數又兜得番個故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過動畫係神既, 一套唔比答案既動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so